{"tid":747701,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"有鬼婆寫左個習近平做主角嘅甜故","createTime":"2018-07-18T14:56:25.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-19T12:08:43.000Z","uid":71008,"like":31,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"b0dfa490764e0db1f90e0c65cfa43f08d890cde6","tid":747701,"uid":71008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-18T14:56:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/18/225528_584e2c9defd5823ae77b230620459ec3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F18%2F225528_584e2c9defd5823ae77b230620459ec3.png&h=bac2a0d5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nShe's a lonely, overworked waitress in a downbeat Chicago pizza joint, and he's the president of the People's Republic of China on a tour of the United States. Their stressful, boring lives are about to heat up like a pizza oven after a chance encounter outside Manny's Pizza Barn. &quot;Call me Xi Dada,&quot; he says. From there, Delanie takes Xi Jinping by the hand and leads him on a whirlwind tour of of Chicago as they struggle to keep their hands off each other."},{"pid":"b7031203cee6f1e69b08bd042407d6e4a65b287d","tid":747701,"uid":163554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-18T14:57:09.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"04765fc78214bc0c7a1177f5532854aa09e1a428","tid":747701,"uid":28195,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-18T15:01:26.000Z","msg":"&quot;Call me Xi Da Da&quot; <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n林鄭濕哂"},{"pid":"b938101b9ce931bec3ac84fc389bee17ec1d3b45","tid":747701,"uid":71008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-18T15:02:58.000Z","msg":"Xi's the One <a href=\"https://www.amazon.com/dp/B01N1XZ33L/ref=cm_sw_r_cp_api_Nz1tBb9YV8VBJ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2Fdp%2FB01N1XZ33L%2Fref%3Dcm_sw_r_cp_api_Nz1tBb9YV8VBJ&d=SCEFF7vn6on4nAu3sYI3NQRJEaK469wi7EMLOMkgk88%3D&h=d9b042e6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.amazon.com/dp/B01N1XZ33L/ref=cm_sw_r_cp_api_Nz1tBb9YV8VBJ</a>"},{"pid":"df80caabc5b76a3bffe6731e5e5de49415bd3278","tid":747701,"uid":71008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"04765fc78214bc0c7a1177f5532854aa09e1a428","tid":747701,"uid":28195,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-18T15:01:26.000Z","msg":"&quot;Call me Xi Da Da&quot; <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n林鄭濕哂"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-18T15:03:44.000Z","msg":"係鬼妹wor"},{"pid":"0e67c0ff3b045463e91438656eb38f75efb71f77","tid":747701,"uid":73443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-18T15:04:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f33d418da842b1fda4864142ea2cb30f79e8918","tid":747701,"uid":71008,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-18T15:06:21.000Z","msg":"As a connoisseur of erotica featuring the paramount leader of the People's Republic of China, I was excited by the prospect of Sandra Coupland's Xi's the One. The cover features a wonderful image of the leader of the world's largest Communist Party (and in my opinion, the best) in all his masculine glory, guaranteed to send even the most rabid advocate of Taiwanese independence into aroused submission. Xi's the One deserves to be widely-published and read as an important supplement to Xi Jinping Thought and as an essential appendix to Xi's own The Governance of China: Volume 1 (please please please Shanghai Press, if you're reading this, release Volume 2 NOW!).<br />\n<br />\nHowever, it is my sad duty to mark down the book due to a number of critical errors that all Xi Jinping erotica should contain as per the constitution of the People's Republic of China:<br />\n<br />\n- No fanny patting.<br />\n- No whispers of harmony.<br />\n- Completely fails to highlight the benefits of the One Road One Belt Initiative.<br />\n<br />\nHence: 3 shining socialist stars out of five. Only the glorious flag of the PRC deserves the full five stars."},{"pid":"03563d43abc50a4f96c0e301ab782de93520e373","tid":747701,"uid":137725,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-18T15:06:28.000Z","msg":"習鄭濕哂<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98f7acd5381db9f9aeb6a08a93beb973915a7ddb","tid":747701,"uid":194630,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-18T15:06:55.000Z","msg":"笑到仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2aa32f002159e0cc5cbf53ead5a267b3b7308dca","tid":747701,"uid":28195,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-18T15:14:00.000Z","msg":"我竟然買咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/18/231308_f4102f7bc2fef4d3b8c21d2add142136.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F18%2F231308_f4102f7bc2fef4d3b8c21d2add142136.png&h=500e6f86&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4aebf00a3f18f1a5db7ae80211074e234fe597a7","tid":747701,"uid":140802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-18T15:14:35.000Z","msg":"佢會唔會被消失<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8545be030310f8c274456094a3a6ee3d067f87d","tid":747701,"uid":71008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2aa32f002159e0cc5cbf53ead5a267b3b7308dca","tid":747701,"uid":28195,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-18T15:14:00.000Z","msg":"我竟然買咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/18/231308_f4102f7bc2fef4d3b8c